---
description: How to explain setup and testing to the non-technical owner
globs: ["docs/**/*", "README.md"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use numbered click-by-click instructions.
- Define technical terms in one sentence.
- Never say “configure it” without exact steps.
- Distinguish actions the agent completed from actions the user must perform.
- Keep phase summaries short and show both phase-count and weighted progress.
